questionsAndAnswers.question: Who will own the app ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Once the app is complete and delivered to you than you'll be the sole owner of the app.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What other costs will be there except development cost ?

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the apps uploaded on app store ?
